<sect1 id="fantasdic-dictionaries">
<title>Dictionaries</title>

<sect2 id="fantasdic-dictionaries-source">
    <title>Source</title>
    
    <figure id="fantasdic-dictionaries-source-fig">
        <title>Source tab</title>
        <screenshot>
            <mediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                    <imagedata                             
                            fileref="figures/fantasdic-dictionaries-source.png"
                            format="PNG"/>
                </imageobject>
                <textobject><phrase>Shows the Source 
                        tab</phrase></textobject>
            </mediaobject>
        </screenshot>
    </figure>

    <para>To add a dictionary:</para>

    <orderedlist>
        <listitem><para>Edit the <guilabel>Name</guilabel>
        entry.</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Choose the source type using the
        <guilabel>source</guilabel> combobox.</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Choose between <guilabel>Search all databases</guilabel>
        and <guilabel>Search selected databases</guilabel>.</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Edit the attributes of the selected
        source.</para></listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para>Different source types use different attributes. This
        is the list of available attributes per source type:</para>
    
    <informaltable frame="all">
        <tgroup cols="2" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
            <thead>
                <row valign="top">
                    <entry><para>Source</para></entry>
                    <entry><para>Attributes</para></entry>
                    <entry><para>Related links</para></entry>
                </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <row valign="top">
                    <entry><para>DICT dictionary Server</para></entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Hostname: the hostname of the dictionary
                        server</para>
                        <para>Port: the port of the dictionary server</para>
                        <para>Username: an optional username</para>
                        <para>Password: an optional password</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry><para><ulink url="http://www.dict.org"
                    >dict.org</ulink></para></entry>
                </row>
                <row valign="top">
                    <entry><para>EDICT file</para></entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para>File: the path of the EDICT file</para>
                        <para>Encoding: the encoding of the EDICT file</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry><para><ulink
url="http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/j_edict.html"
                                        >EDICT</ulink></para></entry>
                </row>
                <row valign="top">
                    <entry><para>Google Translate</para></entry>
                    <entry><para>none</para></entry>
                    <entry></entry>
                </row>
            </tbody>
    </tgroup>
      </informaltable>
</sect2>

<sect2 id="fantasdic-dictionaries-databases">
    <title>Databases</title>
    
    <figure id="fantasdic-dictionaries-databases-fig">
        <title>Databases</title>
        <screenshot>
            <mediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                    <imagedata
                             
fileref="figures/fantasdic-dictionaries-databases.png"
                              format="PNG"/>
                </imageobject>
                <textobject><phrase>Shows the Databases
                        tab</phrase></textobject>
            </mediaobject>
        </screenshot>
    </figure>

    <para>It is possible to select the databases to use when a word is
    looked up using the dictionary.</para>

    <orderedlist>
        <listitem><para>Select one or more databases in <guilabel>Available
        databases</guilabel>.</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Move them to <guilabel>Selected
        databases</guilabel>.</para></listitem>        
      </orderedlist>
    
</sect2>

<sect2 id="fantasdic-dictionaries-fonts">
    <title>Fonts</title>
    
    <figure id="fantasdic-dictionaries-fonts-fig">
        <title>Fonts tab</title>
        <screenshot>
            <mediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                    <imagedata
                             
fileref="figures/fantasdic-dictionaries-fonts.png"
                              format="PNG"/>
                </imageobject>
                <textobject><phrase>Shows the Fonts
                        tab</phrase></textobject>
            </mediaobject>
        </screenshot>
    </figure>

    <para>To change the font name and size used for displaying the results and
    for printing, perform the following steps:</para>
    
    <orderedlist>
        <listitem><para>Click on the <guilabel>Font</guilabel>
                button</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Select the desired font and size</para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>Click <guibutton>Ok</guibutton></para></listitem>
      </orderedlist>
</sect2>

